data.description: POOL HOME in popular Marion Oaks! Spacious 1709 sq ft 4 bedroom, 2 bath, 1 car garage pool home on .18 acre . Welcoming double door at entrance into the living room with amazing built in shelving, updated kitchen with all appliances 5 years old or less, master bedroom has a walk in closet and a bonus room attached that could be an office, nursery, exercise room, sitting room, so many possibilities! NEW ROOF 2023, NEW WINDOWS 2023, nearly NEW HVAC 2022, nearly NEW ELECTRICAL PANEL 2022, POOL ENCLOSURE RESCREEN 2021, REFINISHED POOL 2018, POOL PUMP REPLACEMENT and pool light 2021. The lower level of the pool screen has the pet screen installed. THIS is a GREAT OPPORTUNITY, you just cannot get this sq footage along with a pool in new construction at this price point in Marion Oaks! An older home like this one, updated well, is a great option. Come make this home yours! Ready for occupancy!
